CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1945, pg. 5 reads: "Good Deed - Members of the Shadyside Community Club entertained Deshon Hospital veterans last Thursday evening in home of Mrs. Isadore Reid...Lower photo: members of the club relax and pose for the Courier photographer. Organized less than six months ago, they have as their main purpose the entertaining of the Deshon boys. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of members of the Shadyside Community Club with four men, and nine women, including woman on right wearing dark dress with light colored yoke, posed in home of Isadore Reid
